snippet.title: Corporate Lifestyle Simulator - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Official launch trailer for the "Zombies." expansion pack called "Corporate Lifestyle Simulator" that adds new levels, new weapons, completely redesigned boss fights, new music, gamepad support, and a tonne of new features.

Available exclusively on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/261880/

Background Music:  https://bignic.bandcamp.com/track/corporate-lifestyle-simulator-trailer
